===2convert_TIFFF_TIF_js===

Shell script generates fiji macros doing the [http://openspim.org/Pre-processing pre-processing] of spim data. Specify complete path to data and an integer for each data directory as second parameter (cf. Usage). These macros are stored in the folder „../macros/converter“.

